Package Tekiz._DPSCalculator._DPSCalculator.services.aggregation

Class ModifierAggregationService<V>

java.lang.Object
Tekiz._DPSCalculator._DPSCalculator.services.aggregation.ModifierAggregationService<V>
Type Parameters:
V - The type of value used for the modifier effects, such as Integer or Double.
@Service public class ModifierAggregationService<V> extends Object
A service that retrieves and returns all known modifiers. This service also applies values to "ADDITIONAL_CONTEXT_REQUIRED" ModifierTypes and retrieve all modifiers of a given type.
